🐞 FormaFit Website – Bug Reports
🔴 Bug #001: Full Name Field Accepts Numbers and Special Characters
- Severity: High
- Steps to Reproduce:
- Navigate to the registration form
- Enter “John@123” in the Full Name field
- Submit the form
- Expected Result: Validation error for invalid characters
- Actual Result: Form accepts input and proceeds
- Notes: No regex validation applied

🟠 Bug #002: Phone Number Field Allows Less Than 10 Digits
- Severity: Medium
- Steps to Reproduce:
- Enter “98765” in the Phone Number field
- Submit the form
- Expected Result: Error message for incomplete number
- Actual Result: Form accepts and submits
- Notes: No length check enforced

🟠 Bug #003: Email Field Accepts Invalid Format
- Severity: Medium
- Steps to Reproduce:
- Enter “userexample.com” (missing @)
- Submit the form
- Expected Result: Validation error
- Actual Result: Form accepts input
- Notes: Regex pattern missing or misconfigured

🟢 Bug #004: Password Field Does Not Enforce Complexity
- Severity: Low
- Steps to Reproduce:
- Enter “password” (no uppercase, number, or symbol)
- Submit the form
- Expected Result: Error for weak password
- Actual Result: Form accepts password
- Notes: No complexity rules applied

🔴 Bug #005: Submit Button Enabled Without Required Fields
- Severity: High
- Steps to Reproduce:
- Leave all fields blank
- Observe that Submit button is clickable
- Expected Result: Button should be disabled
- Actual Result: Button remains active
- Notes: Missing front-end validation logic
